<p local-id=3D"d894b199af37">Authenticated user context</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"7c8b9dd8-628a-45a4-b60d-19d2b930f65b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ecd7b2490366">Token / session ref</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"6a6ddfab-ccb0-4b39-a656-93717c0ce9f1" class=3D"conflue=
