<ul local-id=3D"2f40b576-8e8d-42c2-9d58-ce27ef38f329">
<li local-id=3D"3ad53626-0b20-4d9b-9d06-e6d662328771">
<p local-id=3D"9ee6704668ce">Component must fail gracefully and surface a c=
lear error state if required initialization parameters are missing or malfo=
rmed =E2=80=94 it must not silently render an incomplete flow</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"5c49b562ad03" id=3D"EmbeddableKYCandRiskReviewUI-Client-Sid=
eEventContract">Client-Side Event Contract</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"bc0cb6d6-fe90-4301-aa47-518eb68fa886">
<li local-id=3D"95d63204-fd5a-43a7-ac8f-aba839ec250d">
<p local-id=3D"7e8b59de5519">Component emits the following events to the ho=
st application:</p></li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"f3=
0fe266-5426-4ad6-923e-2a52517705b7" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"32aba4c5-afe2-4b23-8975-9ca372e4b634">
<th data-local-id=3D"b5f5ddfe-bc69-4777-8caa-00d3e2a94e1b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"499857a8a2a1">Event</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"7a769cdd-08d9-41e3-840d-5d2daaca29dd" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"5e1e66fda2f4">When</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"05439e92-f7c0-4bcf-8492-9fb13bec7e0c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"5a589bd8e11a">Payload</p></th>
</tr>
